fields.title: About Us
fields.summary: Camelot! Bring her forward! Where'd you get the coconuts? Burn her! You don't frighten us, English pig-dogs!
fields.contents:
Found them? In Mercia?! The coconut's tropical! The swallow may fly south with the sun.

Camelot! Bring her forward! Where'd you get the coconuts? Burn her! You don't frighten us, English pig-dogs! Go and boil your bottoms, sons of a silly person! I blow my nose at you, so-called Ah-thoor Keeng, you and all your silly English K-n-n-n-n-n-n-n-niggits! You don't frighten us, English pig-dogs! Go and boil your bottoms, sons of a silly person! I blow my nose at you, so-called Ah-thoor Keeng, you and all your silly English K-n-n-n-n-n-n-n-niggits!

fields.title: What we Believe
fields.summary: I'm surprised you had the courage to take the responsibility yourself. Red Five standing by. Don't act so surprised, Your Highness. You weren't on any mercy mission this time. Several transmissions were beamed to this ship by Rebel spies.
fields.contents:
As you wish. What?! In my experience, there is no such thing as luck. Dantooine. They're on Dantooine. She must have hidden the plans in the escape pod. Send a detachment down to retrieve them, and see to it personally, Commander. There'll be no one to stop us this time!

* All right. Well, take care of yourself, Han. I guess that's what you're best at, ain't it?
* I'm trying not to, kid.
* Alderaan? I'm not going to Alderaan. I've got to go home. It's late, I'm in for it as it is.

fields.title: Location
fields.summary: There's nothing for me here now. I want to learn the ways of the Force and be a Jedi, like my father before me. You are a part of the Rebel Alliance and a traitor! Take her away!
fields.contents: Remember, a Jedi can feel the Force flowing through him. Alderaan? I'm not going to Alderaan. I've got to go home. It's late, I'm in for it as it is. No! Alderaan is peaceful. We have no weapons. You can't possibly… She must have hidden the plans in the escape pod. Send a detachment down to retrieve them, and see to it personally, Commander. There'll be no one to stop us this time!

fields.title: Staff
fields.summary: Son, as your lawyer, I declare y'all are in a 12-piece bucket o' trouble. But I done struck you a deal: Five hours of community service cleanin' up that ol' mess you caused.
fields.contents: When will that be? Maybe I love you so much I love you no matter who you are pretending to be. We'll go deliver this crate like professionals, and then we'll go home. Bender! Ship! Stop bickering or I'm going to come back there and change your opinions manually!
